lead_paragraph: Atletico Madrid missed a chance to go top of La Liga on Saturday after they slumped to a 2-0 defeat at Real Sociedad, with  Carlos Vela scoring one penalty and winning another.

headline.print_headline: Vela Drives Sociedad to 2-0 Win Over Atletico
headline.main: Vela Drives Sociedad to 2-0 Win Over Atletico
